*Njenom* devojci je donela poklon za rođendan. (She brought a gift for her daughter's birthday.)

Kad je videla *njenom* stanju, nije mogla da sakrije suze. (When she saw her condition, she couldn't hide her tears.)

*Njenom* dolasku je počela da se smeje. (She started laughing upon her arrival.)

Kad je ugledala *njenom* licu, shvatila je da joj nešto nije u redu. (When she saw her face, she realized something wasn't right.)

Bio je veoma srećan kada je čuo *njenom* glasu. (He was very happy when he heard her voice.)